        <item>
            <title>Xpeng X9 纯电 MPV 右軚版抵港，抢先睇车身、内笼设计、详细规格</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/19/xpeng-x9/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xpeng-x9</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/19/xpeng-x9/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 07:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[XPENG X9]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1270076</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>XPENG 小鹏汽车推出的全新右軚版本纯电 MPV X9 今日正式在香港上市，这新款电动车结合现代化外观设计、科技功能和舒适的内笼设计，专为追求豪华与科技并存的车主而设，结合商务和家庭用途，亦适合香港用家。</p><p><a title="_DSC2616" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562519/in/album-72177720321318549" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562519_21d11bc671_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2616" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2620" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54074358127/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54074358127_69dbc8b24c_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2620" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>XPENG X9 外观设计延续了小鹏汽车一贯的科技感及豪华感。这款 MPV 的车身尺寸为 5293 x 1988 x 1785 mm，车身高度 1.78 米专为进出香港停车场而设。车身搭载了全球唯一的主动式后轮转向技术，能够使转弯直径缩小至 10.8 米，转角最大达到 ±5°，使驾驶更加灵活。配备的智能双腔空气悬挂系统，则可以根据车速自动调整车身高度，最多达 90 毫米，以应对不同路况。</p><p><a title="_DSC2624" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495568/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495568_d3217fc99d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2624" width="1024" height="611" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC2628" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495548/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495548_fb35d15499_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2628" width="1024" height="586" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>X9 内部设计上追求空间感及灵活性，车厢拥有 82 平方尺（7.7 平方米）的宽敞空间，是同级车中最大的车型之一。车内配备了 1,100 毫米的超长电动滑轨和 180 毫米的中央通道，使乘客能轻松移动。而第三排座椅则可一键电动收纳，腾出一个 1.8 米 x 1.6 米的大平台，进一步增强了车内的灵活性和空间利用率。此外行李箱采用下沉式设计，最大容量可达 2,554 公升，足够放置四个标准高尔夫球袋，极大提升了实用性。</p><p><a title="_DSC2630" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238296/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238296_446a99d656_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2630" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2632" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238266/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238266_7eb2d54e9c_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2632" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2640" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075689230/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075689230_54144629ef_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2640" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2651" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562469/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562469_548241d8e6_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2651" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2654" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238276/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238276_2c85bcb1e1_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2654" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2658" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238231/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238231_60fc4c904a_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2658" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2665" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562494/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562494_a08710d7fd_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2665" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2666" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238221/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238221_e2fcb701b7_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2666" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>X9 中控台设计简洁，搭载了 21.4 吋的超大显示屏幕，为驾驶者提供全面的信息显示，让驾驶体验更加直观。同时，车内还设有升级选配的零重力座椅，使长途驾驶更加舒适。此外，车内还配备了 0 至 50°C 的冷热一体式雪柜，为乘客提供便利。</p><p><a title="_DSC2669" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238251/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238251_f34fe92051_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2669" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2674" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54074358072/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54074358072_424ac54b7b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2674" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2676" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495483/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495483_1069905386_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2676" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2680" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562439/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562439_bbd2212b98_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2680" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2684" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562384/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562384_bfa4896a1e_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2684" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2689" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495493/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495493_7d881e0dd2_b.jpg" alt="_DSC2689" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>X9 在科技配置上也不落后，这款车型搭载了 800V 高压 SiC 碳化矽平台，充电效能提升一倍，20 分钟内即可将电池从 10% 充至 80%，有效应对长途和短途的驾驶需求。续航方面，长续航版 X9 的最大续航距离可达 575 公里 (WLTP)，这对于应对日常使用和长途旅行都十分有利。</p><p><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC2700" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075689100/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="