_9caf36c887_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2443" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>在安全配置方面，X9 拥有全球量产最大 12,000 吨位压铸一体式车身，令整车刚度达到 46,000 Nm/deg，确保车身结构的稳定性和耐用性。此外，X9 还配备了 17 项主动安全功能，为驾驶者和乘客提供全面的保护，确保行车安全。同时，X9 亦具备大湾区联保服务，令车主在珠三角地区行驶时更加安心。</p><p><a title="IMG_2445" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54074357967/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54074357967_c61161b315_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2445" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2457" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238071/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238071_9574254a43_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2457" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2466" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075689045/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075689045_c8c8c10e88_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2466" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2469" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075495313/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075495313_b24d752600_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2469" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2479" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238011/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238011_e3297466a1_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2479" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2484" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54074357902/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54074357902_3f0975b666_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2484" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2487" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075562254/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075562254_26704fca74_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2487" width="768" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="IMG_2493" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/54075238026/in/album-72177720321318549/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54075238026_f63cf3ffbc_b.jpg" alt="IMG_2493" width="1024" height="768" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td valign="middle"><b>型号</b></td><td valign="middle"><b>XPENG</b><b>小鹏汽车右軚版明日星舰</b><b>MPV X9</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" valign="middle"><b><span class="Apple-converted-space">        </span></b></td></tr><tr><td valign="middle"><b>电池容量</b><b> (kWh)</b></td><td valign="middle">标准版 84.5</p><p>长续航版 101.5</td></tr><tr><td valign="middle"><b>最大续航距离</b><b> (km) (WLTP combine)</b></td><td valign="middle">标准版 480</p><p>长续航版 575</td></tr><tr><td valign="middle"><b>最大功率</b><b> (kW)</b></td><td valign="middle">235</td></tr><tr><td valign="middle"><b>最大