        <item>
            <title>避开芒亨《人中之龙 8 外传》提前发售，横山昌义：让大家放心狩猎，网民大赞正直</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/19/pirates-in-hawaii/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=pirates-in-hawaii</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/19/pirates-in-hawaii/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 19 Oct 2024 06:00:11 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人中之龙 8 外传]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1270157</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《人中之龙 8 外传 Pirates in Hawaii》原本预定在 2025 年 2 月 28 日发售，但日前系列总监横山昌义宣布，游戏将提前一周于 2 月 21 日推出。而在 SEGA 公布此消息的影片当中，工作室总指挥横山昌义提到「为了大家可以玩到接下来推出的游戏」「大家可以放心狩猎」被网民大赞，表示此举让他们更放心玩齐两款游戏，横山的正直言论也给人好感。</p><p>《人中之龙 8 外传 Pirates in Hawaii》与另一热门大作《Monster Hunter Wilds》发售日期太过接近，令到玩家们颇为苦恼。而 SEGA 人中之龙制作室总指挥横山昌义，决定将他们的游戏提早一星期发售，这已是在游戏界中颇为少见。</p><p>横山昌义在影片中解释，决定提前发售是因为游戏开发进行得非常顺利，他希望玩家能够更早体验新作《人中之龙 8 外传》，然后可以「更安心投入到之后发售的游戏」、「放心去狩猎」。网民对横山这次的决定给予高度评价，玩家指横山在影片中间接提到与《Monster Hunter Wilds》发售日期相撞的情况，坦率的言论让人很有好感；有玩家以为游戏会延期，但看到提前发售的消息感到惊喜；有人原本打算等《人中之龙 8 外传》减价后才购买，现在两款游戏不同日期，可放心买齐两款游戏。有玩家认为作为社会上工作的人，理解到这么多开发者参与的游戏要提前一个星期发售难度很大，对开发团队的努力表示感谢。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270161" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/piratesinhawaii12scr-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/piratesinhawaii12scr-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/piratesinhawaii12scr.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲横山：「让大家更安心玩之后推出的游戏」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270160" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/piratesinhawaii147sc-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/piratesinhawaii147sc-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/piratesinhawaii147sc.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲横山：「&#8230;然后可以好好投入狩猎世界」</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_75211"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WDQNfhKkomo?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_93623"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/T68fs58D6kM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/52adde427201f9cf7c4278387707cc13e9fba626">BuzzFeed</a>, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T68fs58D6kM&amp;t=4s">YouTube</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/19/pirates-in-hawaii/game-channel/">避开芒亨《人中之龙 8 外传》提前发售，横山昌义：让大家放心狩猎，网民大赞正直</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
